text: 1. #IAFBali2018 is the first historical forum which gather government, policy makers, private sectors & related stakeholders from 46 countries to discuss concrete cooperations in strategic sectors. #IndonesiaAfrica (10-11/4) https://t.co/Onq55nMHHu

name: KBRI BEIJING
text: 2.African nations have been friends of Indonesia since a long time ago. The Asia-Africa Conference in Bandung in 1955 was an important milestone for #IndonesiaAfrica #IAFBali2018 https://t.co/BBXlu1WTrx

name: KBRI BEIJING
text: Today in #IAFBali2018, Indonesia and African nations reunite to work together in advancing economic cooperation. The trade volume between Africa and Indonesia in 2017 reached USD 8,84 billion or a 15,25% increase from 2016. #IndonesiaAfrica

name: KBRI BEIJING
text: With the support of more than a 400 million productive age population in Africa & Indonesia. The future of #IndonesiaAfrica economic cooperation is very bright. #IAFBali2018
